				<td colspan="2"><span>New twist to getting into Fear. There are new mobs near zone-in. Ireblind Imp has an utterly HUGE AoE mez that is apparently almost unresistable (-1000 by most reports). He also has some sidekicks called Essence of Rage or somesuch. Ireblind tends to remain near portal. Essences like to chase folks around and shadow-step them. Not sure (yet) if they can see invis or not.
<br />

<br />
He seems to spawn near the zone-in.  Probably for a new GOD quest or the Berserker epic.
<br />

<br />
Fear break-in just got harder. Joy.
